WEBVTT

00:01.000 --> 00:03.379
Mmm. Eyeballs, rats,
bats, vampire teeth.

00:03.436 --> 00:05.438
Boom. Vampire teeth.
Good.

00:05.505 --> 00:07.451
Spiderwebs.
Done.

00:08.408 --> 00:09.910
Fake blood capsules.

00:09.976 --> 00:12.149
They didn't have any.
Really?

00:14.447 --> 00:16.256
That's gross. I love it.

00:16.315 --> 00:18.728
We are throwing a Halloween
party at our house.

00:18.785 --> 00:20.492
It's gonna be
the greatest thing ever.

00:20.553 --> 00:22.590
Someone will die.
Of fun.

00:22.655 --> 00:23.656
And of murder.

00:23.723 --> 00:26.829
There's going to be beer, pumpkins...
Bloody goblins.

00:26.893 --> 00:29.271
Fake ones. It's gonna be awesome.
We have decorations.

00:29.329 --> 00:30.831
Dead people that
we just murdered.

00:30.897 --> 00:34.310
Not murdered, but pictures of
dead people from TV or movies.

00:34.367 --> 00:36.472
Mutilated bodies.
But fake ones.

00:36.536 --> 00:39.983
Candy, dancing, tequila.
All kinds of food and snacks.

00:40.040 --> 00:42.884
Blood orphans.
No blood orphans.

00:42.942 --> 00:45.286
I don't know what that is.

