Twitter accounts,

12:57.076 --> 12:59.955
set each other's
clothes on fire.

13:00.012 --> 13:01.548
There are no rules.

13:04.250 --> 13:05.729
We need to deal with
what's bothering you.

13:05.785 --> 13:07.128
Oh, please,
come into my room.

13:07.186 --> 13:10.133
See, you're angry at me, and
you're not talking about it.

13:10.189 --> 13:14.365
And I'm going to beat you up until
you do, because I'm mature.

13:14.426 --> 13:16.201
What are you... Stop it.

13:16.262 --> 13:20.267
I grew up with five brothers, and
we fought using the Dwyer method,

13:20.332 --> 13:24.872
which was yelling,
wrestling, crying

13:24.937 --> 13:28.111
followed by lots of hugs.

13:28.174 --> 13:29.676
And then more wrestling,
but the fun kind.

13:29.742 --> 13:32.848
And then crying when the fun kind
of wrestling got out of hand.

13:32.912 --> 13:36.450
Can you let me go? Not until
you tell me what's wrong.

13:38.818 --> 13:41.321
Mr. President,
I just want to apologize

13:41.387 --> 13:43.025
for the actions of
that little weasel.

13:43.088 --> 13:46.968
Leslie, I'm a frugal man. I don't
like extravagance or showmanship.

13:47.026 --> 13:49.063
That's why
I cut my own hair.

13:49.128 --> 13:51.540
And it's what's made me
a successful businessman.

13:51.597 --> 13:55.067
So if Entertainment 720 is the
kind of business you trust,

13:55.134 --> 13:58.013
I'm afraid you and I
don't share the same values.

14:07.813 --> 14:08.883
There you are,
you little bastard.

14:08.948 --> 14:10.427
Get out of there
right now.

14:10.482 --> 14:12.689
Leslie, can you do me a favor
and just let me sit here?

14:12.751 --> 14:15.595
Tom, get out of your stupid
limousine hot tub right now,

14:15.654 --> 14:16.997
or we are
no longer friends.

14:17.056 --> 14:18.592
I'm not getting out.

14:18.657 --> 14:20.659
Fine. Then I'm getting in.

14:22.161 --> 14:23.162
Listen to me.

14:23.229 --> 14:24.435
You know what you are?
Get away from me!

14:24.496 --> 14:26.169
You're such a little
selfish punk, okay?

14:26.232 --> 14:27.438
Just because
you want something

14:27.499 --> 14:28.876
