should have
caught that one.

17:35.754 --> 17:38.325
Also, your logo, it's the
worst logo I've ever seen.

17:38.390 --> 17:40.802
It doesn't make any sense.
It's gibberish.

17:40.859 --> 17:43.169
We made some mistakes.

17:44.263 --> 17:48.473
