a big client, and I failed again.

17:48.534 --> 17:50.275
God, it's so embarrassing.

17:50.335 --> 17:54.306
Hey, Tom. You're a smart guy
and charming occasionally.

17:54.373 --> 17:57.320
You're going to have
a lot more good ideas.

17:58.010 --> 17:59.990
Thanks.

18:00.045 --> 18:01.888
I'm sorry I screwed up
your campaign thing.

18:01.947 --> 18:03.756
