Like, tell me about stuff
happening in the house.

18:30.275 --> 18:33.188
Stop referring to my
bedroom as a common space.

18:33.245 --> 18:36.454
Stop using my comforter
for your pillow forts.

18:36.515 --> 18:38.552
Just respect me.

18:38.617 --> 18:40.062
Absolutely.
Really?

18:40.119 --> 18:42.463
Yep. And in return,
I'll only ask for one thing,

18:42.521 --> 18:44.694
